text: Eugenie Briollet (7 November 1900 - 1 May 1985) was a French diver. She competed in the women's 3 metre springboard event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1900 births Category:1985 deaths Category:French female divers Category:Olympic divers of France Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Strasbourg
